321
00:11:28,700 --> 00:11:29,340
Officers,

322
00:11:29,890 --> 00:11:30,690
I didn't do it.

323
00:11:30,740 --> 00:11:31,480
I didn't.

324
00:11:32,150 --> 00:11:32,890
I didn't!

325
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,000
I don't know

326
00:11:35,020 --> 00:11:36,550
