327
00:11:38,220 --> 00:11:41,290
[Criminal Police Brigade]

328
00:11:41,410 --> 00:11:46,230
[Wu Jiang][Transportation]
[National Highway 109]

329
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:55,530
Bai Ju.

330
00:11:56,290 --> 00:11:57,950
The ballistics report is out.

331
00:12:01,220 --> 00:12:02,580
Tests confirm the ballistic markings

332
00:12:02,580 --> 00:12:04,460
