337
00:12:09,770 --> 00:12:11,570
from the Qima'er Gold Mine case.

338
00:12:11,580 --> 00:12:13,710
All were fired from the submitted gun.

339
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:29,910
I told you

340
00:12:29,930 --> 00:12:31,460
that gun really isn't mine.

341
00:12:34,940 --> 00:12:36,700
This is the crime scene photo
showing the gun

342
00:12:36,700 --> 00:12:38,700
