424
00:15:06,340 --> 00:15:06,960
Besides,

425
00:15:07,720 --> 00:15:08,580
the tea and wine

426
00:15:08,580 --> 00:15:09,610
in my trunk

427
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:10,610
