429
00:15:12,790 --> 00:15:14,580
There are cameras
in the company's parking lot.

430
00:15:14,580 --> 00:15:15,560
You can check.

431
00:15:15,690 --> 00:15:16,840
I remember that bag

432
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:18,560
