433
00:15:18,650 --> 00:15:19,190
Did you go

434
00:15:19,220 --> 00:15:21,150
to the Qima'er Gold Mine back then?

435
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,860
Someone is out to get me.

436
00:15:26,980 --> 00:15:27,980
I want a lawyer.

437
00:15:29,330 --> 00:15:30,300
Until then,

438
00:15:30,970 --> 00:15:32,900
I won't answer any more questions.

439
00:15:48,030 --> 00:15:48,580
Captain.

440
00:15:49,330 --> 00:15:51,110
