454
00:16:13,150 --> 00:16:13,650
Here they are.

455
00:16:13,650 --> 00:16:14,450
Here they are.

456
00:16:15,260 --> 00:16:16,010
This is from the garage

457
00:16:16,010 --> 00:16:17,350
at Wu Jiang's complex.

458
00:16:17,380 --> 00:16:17,780
This is from the entrance

459
00:16:17,780 --> 00:16:19,240
