468
00:16:29,130 --> 00:16:30,250
It's nothing.

469
00:16:30,700 --> 00:16:32,360
Back in the Uninhabited Zone,

470
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:33,590
I traveled by day,

471
00:16:33,590 --> 00:16:34,640
