503
00:17:22,980 --> 00:17:23,760
Go, go.

504
00:17:23,790 --> 00:17:24,260
Stop worrying.

505
00:17:24,260 --> 00:17:25,060
Bye, Captain.

506
00:17:34,860 --> 00:17:35,530
Which one

507
