555
00:20:34,810 --> 00:20:35,310
No.

556
00:20:35,940 --> 00:20:37,390
They were all VIP clients.

557
00:20:37,390 --> 00:20:38,000
We couldn't possibly

558
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:38,820
