561
00:20:40,900 --> 00:20:42,160
Even for a few minutes.

562
00:20:44,810 --> 00:20:45,770
I think...

563
00:20:46,700 --> 00:20:47,250
Yes.

564
00:20:47,930 --> 00:20:49,660
Mr. Meng went out to take a call.

565
00:20:49,750 --> 00:20:50,850
