572
00:21:00,640 --> 00:21:01,870
After 10 o'clock, I think.

573
00:21:01,870 --> 00:21:03,270
Right, after 10 o'clock.

574
00:21:09,330 --> 00:21:10,270
Then do you think

575
00:21:10,630 --> 00:21:12,160
