577
00:21:32,290 --> 00:21:32,770
This.

578
00:21:37,700 --> 00:21:38,160
This...

579
00:21:39,010 --> 00:21:39,340
This...

580
00:21:39,340 --> 00:21:41,340
How can you tell anything from this?

581
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:56,070
Mr. Meng,

582
00:21:56,400 --> 00:21:57,930
