589
00:22:28,980 --> 00:22:30,580
Overstepping one's bounds.

590
00:22:40,880 --> 00:22:41,550
Zhao.

591
00:22:45,070 --> 00:22:47,330
How do you pronounce the last character?

592
00:22:49,220 --> 00:22:49,820
Chairman,

593
00:22:50,070 --> 00:22:51,100
may I go

594
00:22:51,140 --> 00:22:52,270
