595
00:23:11,420 --> 00:23:12,250
Do you think

596
00:23:12,860 --> 00:23:14,320
she knows this character?

597
00:23:15,900 --> 00:23:16,470
Yes.

598
00:23:17,080 --> 00:23:17,780
Then why

599
00:23:17,810 --> 00:23:18,870
didn't she tell me?

600
00:23:25,710 --> 00:23:26,850
I told you to get in touch

601
00:23:26,850 --> 00:23:28,980
with that police officer surnamed Bai

602
00:23:29,520 --> 00:23:30,720
to make use of her.

603
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:33,540
Is this how you make use of her?

604
00:23:34,380 --> 00:23:34,910
Mr. Feng.

605
00:23:35,850 --> 00:23:37,000
My idea is simple.

606
00:23:39,140 --> 00:23:41,140
Since they've found Duojie's body,

607
00:23:41,220 --> 00:23:43,000
they won't let this go.

608
00:23:44,370 --> 00:23:46,330
If they investigate me next,

609
00:23:47,710 --> 00:23:49,710
they'll find out about you, Xinhai,

610
00:23:50,780 --> 00:23:51,980
and what happened back then.

611
00:23:51,980 --> 00:23:53,470
Where is Wang Fumin now?

612
00:23:54,970 --> 00:23:55,730
I don't know.

613
00:23:56,880 --> 00:23:58,510
Wang Fumin abandoned his family back then

614
00:23:58,510 --> 00:23:59,910
and ran off to South Asia.

615
00:24:00,090 --> 00:24:01,680
We lost contact years ago.

616
00:24:02,370 --> 00:24:04,170
He has a son in Dongxiang County.

617
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:07,140
I heard the police have already
checked him out.

618
00:24:15,550 --> 00:24:16,480
What do you think

619
00:24:17,130 --> 00:24:18,040
Wu Jiang

620
00:24:18,070 --> 00:24:19,070
will say in there?

621
00:24:20,640 --> 00:24:22,270
His status at Hongyuan

622
00:24:23,090 --> 00:24:24,020
was given by you.

623
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:25,750
Without you,

624
00:24:25,790 --> 00:24:26,920
he would be nothing.

625
00:24:28,350 --> 00:24:29,200
If he doesn't admit

626
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:30,730
to his history at Hongyuan,

627
00:24:31,590 --> 00:24:32,690
he'll have to spill

628
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:33,720
his real history.

629
00:24:34,570 --> 00:24:35,530
Between those matters

630
00:24:35,530 --> 00:24:36,680
and the murder case,

631
00:24:36,700 --> 00:24:38,360
he knows which is more serious

632
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:39,510
perfectly well.

633
00:24:40,050 --> 00:24:40,680
So,

634
00:24:41,500 --> 00:24:43,300
he probably won't say anything.

635
00:24:44,790 --> 00:24:45,790
None of us expected

636
00:24:45,790 --> 00:24:46,720
that he had a murder charge

637
00:24:46,720 --> 00:24:48,270
hanging over him.

638
00:24:49,050 --> 00:24:50,080
I barely even

639
00:24:50,110 --> 00:24:51,110
interacted with him

640
00:24:51,110 --> 00:24:51,760
at work.

641
00:24:52,310 --> 00:24:54,020
On the night Wu Jiang was arrested,

642
00:24:54,020 --> 00:24:56,190
were you eating at the nearby restaurant?

643
00:24:56,190 --> 00:24:56,680
Yes.

644
00:24:57,120 --> 00:24:58,120
In a private room.

645
00:24:58,460 --> 00:24:59,920
Did you go out at any point?

646
00:25:00,030 --> 00:25:01,010
I went out once.

647
00:25:02,250 --> 00:25:03,380
To make a phone call.

648
00:25:04,030 --> 00:25:05,150
Did you leave the restaurant?

649
00:25:05,150 --> 00:25:06,680
No, I made it in the hallway.

650
00:25:07,300 --> 00:25:08,230
Who did you call?

651
00:25:11,980 --> 00:25:13,160
I called a colleague

652
00:25:14,570 --> 00:25:16,300
to discuss the next day's work.

653
00:25:23,460 --> 00:25:24,990
The time of his call matches

654
00:25:25,180 --> 00:25:26,100
the time on the surveillance footage

655
00:25:26,100 --> 00:25:27,140
when Wu Jiang's trunk

656
00:25:27,140 --> 00:25:28,270
was opened.

657
00:25:29,670 --> 00:25:31,070
He had it all planned out.

658
00:25:33,390 --> 00:25:34,650
I'll get the team

659
00:25:34,910 --> 00:25:36,220
to dig deeper into

660
00:25:36,340 --> 00:25:38,030
Meng Yaohui's social connections.

661
00:25:38,030 --> 00:25:38,460
Okay.

662
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:47,230
[Chenlong Coal Mine] [Pass]

663
00:25:49,480 --> 00:25:50,220
Go.

664
00:26:46,710 --> 00:26:47,370
We're here.

665
00:26:47,790 --> 00:26:48,390
Shoot now.

666
00:26:49,460 --> 00:26:50,250
Hurry up.

667
00:26:50,340 --> 00:26:50,850
Okay, okay.

668
00:26:50,850 --> 00:26:52,050
It'll be trouble if we're spotted.

669
00:26:52,050 --> 00:26:53,110
Alright, alright.

670
00:26:59,420 --> 00:27:00,220
Hurry up.

671
00:27:05,250 --> 00:27:05,980
Are you done?

672
00:27:06,240 --> 00:27:07,570
A minute. A minute.

673
00:27:22,790 --> 00:27:24,450
The safety officer is coming.

674
00:27:24,450 --> 00:27:25,450
Hide, quick.

675
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:26,170
Cover me up, come on.

676
00:27:26,170 --> 00:27:26,930
Hurry, hurry.

677
00:27:26,930 --> 00:27:27,370
Quick.

678
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:35,440
Stop, stop.

679
00:27:35,520 --> 00:27:36,090
Stop.

680
00:27:45,320 --> 00:27:46,050
Manager Bai.

681
00:27:46,820 --> 00:27:47,950
Who is in your truck?

682
00:27:49,840 --> 00:27:50,580
Just me.

683
00:27:50,740 --> 00:27:51,400
No one else.

684
00:27:51,790 --> 00:27:52,440
Get out!

685
00:27:54,310 --> 00:27:55,010
Get out!

686
00:28:06,330 --> 00:28:07,060
Manager Bai.

687
00:28:23,110 --> 00:28:24,440
What are you doing here?

688
00:28:28,350 --> 00:28:28,850
Chun.

689
00:28:35,690 --> 00:28:37,220
There are rules in the mine.

690
00:28:37,510 --> 00:28:38,540
You can't bring outsiders in.

691
00:28:38,540 --> 00:28:39,670
Don't you know that?

692
00:28:41,410 --> 00:28:42,540
No, don't blame him.

693
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:44,460
I asked him to do it.

694
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:45,030
As for you,

695
00:28:45,030 --> 00:28:46,430
I'll deal with you later.

696
00:28:53,010 --> 00:28:53,580
I'll tell

697
00:28:53,610 --> 00:28:54,680
your fleet captain

698
00:28:55,040 --> 00:28:56,070
that you have family matters to deal with

699
00:28:56,070 --> 00:28:57,070
and are quitting.

700
00:28:58,040 --> 00:28:59,240
Go pack your things now

701
00:28:59,240 --> 00:29:00,970
and process your resignation.

702
00:29:04,260 --> 00:29:05,590
Thank you, Manager Bai.

703
00:29:16,510 --> 00:29:17,200
See that?

704
00:29:17,600 --> 00:29:18,640
You caused this.

705
00:29:20,590 --> 00:29:21,640
I have a classmate in Inner Mongolia

706
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:22,500
who runs a mine.

707
00:29:22,590 --> 00:29:23,350
I've already recommended him

708
00:29:23,350 --> 00:29:24,280
to go work there.

709
00:29:29,900 --> 00:29:30,670
Take a look.

710
00:29:30,770 --> 00:29:32,170
Look at what you've done.

711
00:29:35,590 --> 00:29:36,220
What?

712
00:29:36,580 --> 00:29:37,600
Didn't you know

713
00:29:37,630 --> 00:29:40,090
the rectification
has turned out like this?

714
00:29:41,330 --> 00:29:42,240
Before, Wu Jiang

715
00:29:42,240 --> 00:29:42,840
was in charge of this.

716
00:29:42,840 --> 00:29:44,300
It's my first time in here.

717
00:29:51,190 --> 00:29:52,250
What are you doing?

718
00:29:52,590 --> 00:29:53,330
Move aside!

719
00:29:53,960 --> 00:29:55,020
What are you doing?

720
00:29:55,750 --> 00:29:57,070
Why did you delete my photos?

721
00:29:57,070 --> 00:29:58,230
These photos can't get out!

722
00:29:58,230 --> 00:29:58,630
You...

723
00:29:59,530 --> 00:30:00,060
Bai Chun,

724
00:30:00,070 --> 00:30:01,420
you've worked in mines for years.

725
00:30:01,420 --> 00:30:02,460
Has the dust blinded you,

726
00:30:02,460 --> 00:30:04,660
or has the slag buried your conscience?

727
00:30:05,250 --> 00:30:06,200
Xinhai just took back

728
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:07,640
management of the small mines.

729
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:09,370
There might be some oversight.

730
00:30:09,530 --> 00:30:11,330
The mining is indeed a bit crude.

731
00:30:11,530 --> 00:30:13,300
Such serious environmental pollution,

732
00:30:13,300 --> 00:30:13,740
and to you,

733
00:30:13,740 --> 00:30:14,720
it's just a casual remark

734
00:30:14,720 --> 00:30:15,700
about crude mining?

735
00:30:15,700 --> 00:30:17,220
Then tell me, what is

736
00:30:17,250 --> 00:30:18,480
management oversight?

737
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:18,960
Open-pit mines

738
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:20,220
are bound to have dust.

739
00:30:20,350 --> 00:30:20,940
But a lot of dust

740
00:30:20,940 --> 00:30:22,340
doesn't mean pollution.

741
00:30:22,370 --> 00:30:23,640
If you go farm in a field,

742
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:24,760
you'll get covered in dirt.

743
00:30:24,760 --> 00:30:25,820
Is that pollution?

744
00:30:29,510 --> 00:30:30,180
Now you're just

745
00:30:30,180 --> 00:30:31,200
being unreasonable, aren't you?

746
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:31,590
I am trying

747
00:30:31,590 --> 00:30:33,190
to reason with you right now.

748
00:30:33,260 --> 00:30:34,160
Could you please drop

749
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:35,400
your ignorant bias?

750
00:30:35,850 --> 00:30:37,500
You always talk about
environmental protection,

751
00:30:37,500 --> 00:30:38,200
keeping fixating

752
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:38,890
on our open-pit mine.

753
00:30:38,890 --> 00:30:39,930
Do you know
what environmental protection is?

754
00:30:39,930 --> 00:30:40,470
I...

755
00:30:40,620 --> 00:30:41,760
A lot of dust

756
00:30:41,790 --> 00:30:42,790
just doesn't look good, that's all.

757
00:30:42,790 --> 00:30:43,310
But at least,

758
00:30:43,310 --> 00:30:44,030
it doesn't leave behind

759
00:30:44,030 --> 00:30:45,520
non-degradable artificial substances

760
00:30:45,520 --> 00:30:46,980
buried deep underground.

761
00:30:47,420 --> 00:30:48,420
Go look abroad.

762
00:30:48,830 --> 00:30:49,520
Many countries

763
00:30:49,520 --> 00:30:50,830
rely mainly on open-pit mining.

764
00:30:50,830 --> 00:30:52,350
I don't care about other countries.

765
00:30:52,350 --> 00:30:53,700
I only care about what's in front of me.

766
00:30:53,700 --> 00:30:55,350
Look for yourself!

767
00:30:55,440 --> 00:30:56,180
The dust situation in your mine

768
00:30:56,180 --> 00:30:57,300
is currently

769
00:30:57,330 --> 00:30:58,480
very serious.

770
00:30:58,500 --> 00:30:59,830
So what if there's dust?

771
00:31:00,250 --> 00:31:00,570
Back when

772
00:31:00,570 --> 00:31:01,520
you entered Bolamula,

773
00:31:01,520 --> 00:31:02,640
it was also dusty inside.

774
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:04,180
There were sandstorms every other day.

775
00:31:04,180 --> 00:31:05,840
Why didn't you choke to death?

776
00:31:10,630 --> 00:31:11,290
Move aside!

777
00:31:11,680 --> 00:31:12,680
Give it back to me!

778
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:15,960
I shouldn't have come here

779
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:17,490
to meddle in your business.

780
00:31:17,640 --> 00:31:18,480
I should have let the security team

781
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:19,280
deal with you.

782
00:31:19,380 --> 00:31:20,910
If you have energy to spare,

783
00:31:21,590 --> 00:31:23,120
care more about your child.

784
00:31:29,250 --> 00:31:30,180
Bring the car up.

785
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:31,370
Take him away.

786
00:31:40,550 --> 00:31:41,030
Come in.

787
00:31:56,450 --> 00:31:57,270
Who are you?

788
00:31:58,100 --> 00:31:59,100
Hello, Mr. Wu.

789
00:31:59,240 --> 00:31:59,790
I am the lawyer

790
00:31:59,790 --> 00:32:01,250
Mr. Feng arranged for you.

791
00:32:01,290 --> 00:32:02,310
My name is Xu Quan.

792
00:32:03,680 --> 00:32:05,540
I haven't seen you at the company.

793
00:32:05,750 --> 00:32:06,220
Mr. Wu,

794
00:32:06,240 --> 00:32:07,750
there seems to be a misunderstanding.

795
00:32:07,750 --> 00:32:09,210
I am not a Xinhai employee.

796
00:32:11,860 --> 00:32:13,190
I've checked your case.

797
00:32:13,510 --> 00:32:15,310
There is still room for defense.

798
00:32:15,520 --> 00:32:16,920
My suggestion is that...

799
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:20,530
you plead guilty first.

800
00:32:20,660 --> 00:32:21,740
In court,

801
00:32:21,780 --> 00:32:23,760
you insist that you confessed voluntarily

802
00:32:23,760 --> 00:32:24,820
and have repented.

803
00:32:25,010 --> 00:32:26,730
Just stick to this point.

804
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:28,700
Maybe...

805
00:32:30,350 --> 00:32:32,080
you'll get life imprisonment.

806
00:32:34,980 --> 00:32:35,780
You can leave.

807
00:32:36,300 --> 00:32:37,300
I don't need this.

808
00:32:37,480 --> 00:32:38,160
Mr. Wu.

809
00:32:40,010 --> 00:32:41,810
This is also what Mr. Feng wants.

810
00:32:43,410 --> 00:32:44,540
What does that mean?

811
00:32:46,760 --> 00:32:48,490
What does the boss mean by this?

812
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:51,140
Everyone knows perfectly well

813
00:32:51,140 --> 00:32:52,220
who owns that gun.

814
00:32:52,470 --> 00:32:53,800
What are they doing now?

815
00:32:54,040 --> 00:32:55,300
Pinning it on me?

816
00:32:56,350 --> 00:32:57,140
If I'm not doing a good job,

817
00:32:57,140 --> 00:32:58,500
just fire me.

818
00:32:58,820 --> 00:33:00,510
Why go through all this trouble?

819
00:33:00,510 --> 00:33:02,070
Mr. Feng asked me to tell you

820
00:33:02,650 --> 00:33:04,850
to cooperate with me with peace of mind.

821
00:33:04,980 --> 00:33:06,090
As for things outside,

822
00:33:06,090 --> 00:33:07,020
no need to worry.

823
00:33:07,810 --> 00:33:09,180
As for your family,

824
00:33:09,500 --> 00:33:11,470
the company will take good care of them

825
00:33:11,470 --> 00:33:13,200
and do your filial duty for you.

826
00:33:30,460 --> 00:33:31,500
I've read the draft

827
00:33:31,500 --> 00:33:32,470
you wrote.

828
00:33:33,140 --> 00:33:34,540
It was written very well.

829
00:33:36,530 --> 00:33:37,670
Then why did you

830
00:33:37,700 --> 00:33:38,440
tell our Chief Editor

831
00:33:38,440 --> 00:33:39,440
not to publish it?

832
00:33:41,030 --> 00:33:41,660
In here,

833
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:42,680
regarding Chenlong's rectification,

834
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:43,270
the details described

835
00:33:43,270 --> 00:33:44,530
are true, aren't they?

836
00:33:45,350 --> 00:33:46,210
Reporter Shao.

837
00:33:47,330 --> 00:33:49,590
Does truth represent the whole picture?

838
00:33:50,330 --> 00:33:51,160
How much of their work

839
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:52,530
did you actually see?

840
00:33:53,020 --> 00:33:54,680
Do you have any factual basis?

841
00:33:55,880 --> 00:33:56,740
Actually,

842
00:33:56,770 --> 00:33:57,880
I took photos at the time.

843
00:33:57,880 --> 00:33:58,900
But later...

844
00:33:59,810 --> 00:34:00,590
Come in.

845
00:34:01,290 --> 00:34:02,220
Director Huang.

846
00:34:02,970 --> 00:34:04,230
Mr. Feng, you're here.

847
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:06,460
Reporter Shao is here too.

848
00:34:07,400 --> 00:34:09,000
Were you doing an interview?

849
00:34:09,340 --> 00:34:09,850
Should I

850
00:34:09,880 --> 00:34:11,250
excuse myself for a moment?

851
00:34:11,250 --> 00:34:12,920
Just understanding the situation.

852
00:34:12,920 --> 00:34:14,500
Mr. Feng, you came at the right time.

853
00:34:14,500 --> 00:34:15,340
Let Reporter Shao

854
00:34:15,340 --> 00:34:16,690
interview you properly.

855
00:34:16,690 --> 00:34:18,420
Reporter Shao, what do you say?

856
00:34:18,940 --> 00:34:19,500
Come, come.

857
00:34:19,500 --> 00:34:20,260
Please sit.

858
00:34:20,290 --> 00:34:21,690
Reporter Shao, sit here.

859
00:34:23,230 --> 00:34:24,080
Mr. Feng.

860
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:25,940
Reporter Shao

861
00:34:25,940 --> 00:34:27,520
is very concerned

862
00:34:27,550 --> 00:34:28,719
about our Tianduo coal industry.

863
00:34:28,719 --> 00:34:29,380
We were just

864
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:30,800
talking about Chenlong.

865
00:34:30,860 --> 00:34:31,590
Look at this.

866
00:34:44,690 --> 00:34:46,480
This really is my oversight.

867
00:34:47,710 --> 00:34:49,230
The head of Chenlong

868
00:34:49,300 --> 00:34:50,590
has had some issues recently.

869
00:34:50,590 --> 00:34:52,449
So the staff got out of hand.

870
00:34:53,600 --> 00:34:54,210
Once the new management

871
00:34:54,210 --> 00:34:55,420
is in place,

872
00:34:55,440 --> 00:34:56,770
I promise we'll enforce

873
00:34:57,210 --> 00:34:58,410
strict regulations.

874
00:34:58,490 --> 00:35:00,030
As long as it's cleared up.

875
00:35:00,940 --> 00:35:01,820
Rectification

876
00:35:02,420 --> 00:35:03,360
takes time.

877
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:06,040
Director Huang.

878
00:35:06,570 --> 00:35:07,720
I brought

879
00:35:07,770 --> 00:35:08,940
a photo album today.

880
00:35:11,980 --> 00:35:13,040
Since you're here,

881
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:14,260
Reporter Shao,

882
00:35:14,290 --> 00:35:15,690
please give some advice.

883
00:35:16,420 --> 00:35:17,550
I wouldn't call it advice.

884
00:35:17,550 --> 00:35:18,070
Thank you.

885
00:35:18,070 --> 00:35:18,530
Reporter Shao,

886
00:35:18,530 --> 00:35:19,710
you might not know

887
00:35:20,360 --> 00:35:22,130
that Mr. Feng likes photography.

888
00:35:22,130 --> 00:35:22,760
Whenever he's free,

889
00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:24,530
he goes out to shoot nature.

890
00:35:25,050 --> 00:35:25,940
He's also

891
00:35:26,030 --> 00:35:27,500
the Honorary Chairman

892
00:35:27,530 --> 00:35:29,990
of the Tianduo Photographers Association.

893
00:35:30,150 --> 00:35:31,630
Several of these photos

894
00:35:31,730 --> 00:35:32,710
are award-winning,

895
00:35:32,710 --> 00:35:33,280
and they really capture

896
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:34,740
the beauty of our plateau.

897
00:35:41,640 --> 00:35:43,820
[Tianduo Commercial Bank]
[One million Yuan only]

898
00:35:44,590 --> 00:35:45,590
What do you think?

899
00:36:08,530 --> 00:36:09,280
Great shots,

900
00:36:09,370 --> 00:36:10,700
but don't take any more.

901
00:36:12,170 --> 00:36:13,030
Reporter Shao,

902
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:14,690
what do you mean by that?

903
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:19,150
If I'm not mistaken,

904
00:36:19,290 --> 00:36:20,350
this is a photo

905
00:36:20,380 --> 00:36:21,940
of Mount Chawuma, right?

906
00:36:23,620 --> 00:36:25,620
You have a sharp eye, Reporter Shao.

907
00:36:26,170 --> 00:36:27,510
And for this shot,

908
00:36:27,650 --> 00:36:29,450
you didn't use a telephoto lens.

909
00:36:30,010 --> 00:36:30,880
You must have driven

910
00:36:30,880 --> 00:36:31,880
right up to the mountain

911
00:36:31,880 --> 00:36:33,070
and used a medium-wide

912
00:36:33,070 --> 00:36:34,300
or a wide-angle lens.

913
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:39,160
Right?

914
00:36:46,690 --> 00:36:47,760
The landscape of Mount Chawuma

915
00:36:47,760 --> 00:36:48,800
is unique

916
00:36:49,110 --> 00:36:50,660
because the sandy surface

917
00:36:50,690 --> 00:36:52,220
is covered in black gravel.

918
00:36:54,170 --> 00:36:54,730
This gravel,

919
00:36:54,730 --> 00:36:56,260
after years of weathering,

920
00:36:56,260 --> 00:36:57,900
forms a hard crust.

921
00:36:58,260 --> 00:36:59,920
Once crushed by tires,

922
00:37:00,090 --> 00:37:01,230
the landscape won't recover

923
00:37:01,230 --> 00:37:02,390
for over 100 years.

924
00:37:10,290 --> 00:37:11,120
Reporters

925
00:37:11,640 --> 00:37:13,500
should stick to the facts.

926
00:37:14,760 --> 00:37:16,340
You didn't see it yourself.

927
00:37:17,190 --> 00:37:18,450
Making such a judgment

928
00:37:18,650 --> 00:37:20,010
is a bit rash, isn't it?

929
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:21,800
You have to be responsible

930
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:23,440
for what you say.

931
00:37:24,590 --> 00:37:25,460
I didn't see it.

932
00:37:26,590 --> 00:37:28,190
But my conscience did.

933
00:37:29,050 --> 00:37:29,860
Whether you went there or not,

934
00:37:29,860 --> 00:37:31,150
you know the truth.

935
00:37:50,860 --> 00:37:51,460
Farewell.

936
00:37:53,010 --> 00:37:53,870
Reporter Shao.

937
00:37:59,330 --> 00:38:00,270
We welcome you

938
00:38:00,610 --> 00:38:01,670
to Tianduo.

939
00:38:01,950 --> 00:38:02,420
If you can

940
00:38:02,420 --> 00:38:03,880
give our coal companies

941
00:38:03,900 --> 00:38:05,450
more positive publicity,

942
00:38:05,630 --> 00:38:06,400
I believe

943
00:38:06,500 --> 00:38:07,230
Mr. Feng and I

944
00:38:07,250 --> 00:38:08,640
will fully cooperate.

945
00:38:09,320 --> 00:38:10,000
But if you

946
00:38:10,020 --> 00:38:12,020
keep writing articles like this...

947
00:38:15,090 --> 00:38:16,090
I heard you're close

948
00:38:16,090 --> 00:38:17,730
to Mayor Lin.

949
00:38:18,050 --> 00:38:18,800
Why don't you

950
00:38:18,900 --> 00:38:20,270
ask him what he thinks?

951
00:38:32,760 --> 00:38:33,440
Mayor Lin.

952
00:38:40,730 --> 00:38:41,540
Uncle Lin.

953
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:42,510
Shao,

954
00:38:42,630 --> 00:38:43,400
what are you doing here?

955
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:45,000
Why didn't you come to the house?

956
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:45,710
Last time

957
00:38:45,950 --> 00:38:46,980
at the stadium...

958
00:38:49,460 --> 00:38:51,390
Didn't you get altitude sickness?

959
00:38:51,860 --> 00:38:53,720
Your Auntie Zhu gave me an earful.

960
00:38:53,820 --> 00:38:54,940
Come on, let's go home.

961
00:38:54,940 --> 00:38:55,630
Uncle Lin.

962
00:38:57,860 --> 00:38:58,390
Was it you

963
00:38:58,400 --> 00:38:59,600
who blocked my draft?

964
00:39:04,920 --> 00:39:05,650
Why?

965
00:39:10,010 --> 00:39:10,670
Shao,

966
00:39:11,320 --> 00:39:11,790
Tianduo

967
00:39:11,820 --> 00:39:13,190
looks good right now,

968
00:39:14,270 --> 00:39:15,880
but there are very few

969
00:39:15,900 --> 00:39:17,010
truly high-quality enterprises.

970
00:39:17,010 --> 00:39:17,720
Moreover,

971
00:39:17,850 --> 00:39:20,090
among the black, white,
and red industries,

972
00:39:20,090 --> 00:39:21,690
regarding the distribution,

973
00:39:21,690 --> 00:39:23,320
the black industry is the pillar.

974
00:39:23,320 --> 00:39:24,290
If your report

975
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:25,170
gets out,

976
00:39:25,460 --> 00:39:26,060
really...

977
00:39:27,520 --> 00:39:29,320
If it really brings down Xinhai,

978
00:39:29,780 --> 00:39:31,240
how will the city develop?

979
00:39:31,260 --> 00:39:31,990
Tourism?

980
00:39:33,310 --> 00:39:34,910
I said this over 10 years ago.

981
00:39:35,130 --> 00:39:36,070
If anyone wants

982
00:39:36,090 --> 00:39:37,700
to come here for tourism,

983
00:39:37,810 --> 00:39:38,810
before they come,

984
00:39:38,930 --> 00:39:40,930
I need to build the hospitals first.

985
00:39:41,230 --> 00:39:42,900
So we just ignore the environment?

986
00:39:42,900 --> 00:39:43,760
If we just let it

987
00:39:43,760 --> 00:39:44,890
continue like this,

988
00:39:45,200 --> 00:39:45,650
in the future,

989
00:39:45,650 --> 00:39:47,130
it will take more time and money

990
00:39:47,130 --> 00:39:48,240
to restore the environment.

991
00:39:48,240 --> 00:39:49,040
By then, we...

992
00:39:49,050 --> 00:39:51,110
Environmental protection is right,

993
00:39:51,480 --> 00:39:52,130
but

994
00:39:52,920 --> 00:39:54,510
it must be done gradually.

995
00:39:56,090 --> 00:39:56,730
So you're saying

996
00:39:56,730 --> 00:39:57,880
the city allows Xinhai

997
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:59,280
to conduct such messy...

998
00:40:01,530 --> 00:40:02,570
rectification?

999
00:40:02,680 --> 00:40:03,650
Of course.

1000
00:40:03,760 --> 00:40:05,820
If there are problems, we solve them.

1001
00:40:07,530 --> 00:40:07,930
You...

1002
00:40:09,420 --> 00:40:10,520
If a report like yours

1003
00:40:10,520 --> 00:40:11,330
gets out,

1004
00:40:12,030 --> 00:40:13,090
and if the chain reaction

1005
00:40:13,090 --> 00:40:14,290
can't be controlled,

1006
00:40:14,440 --> 00:40:15,820
then how much tax revenue

1007
00:40:15,820 --> 00:40:17,090
will the city lose?

1008
00:40:17,330 --> 00:40:17,910
Have you

1009
00:40:17,940 --> 00:40:18,970
considered this

1010
00:40:19,230 --> 00:40:20,260
as a reporter?

1011
00:40:22,970 --> 00:40:23,890
And as you saw

1012
00:40:23,910 --> 00:40:24,770
at the meeting,

1013
00:40:25,800 --> 00:40:26,930
my opinion actually

1014
00:40:26,940 --> 00:40:27,950
doesn't align

1015
00:40:27,970 --> 00:40:28,980
with Mayor Wang's.

1016
00:40:28,980 --> 00:40:29,670
But

1017
00:40:29,780 --> 00:40:30,760
I'm about to retire,

1018
00:40:30,760 --> 00:40:31,830
so I can't openly

1019
00:40:31,850 --> 00:40:33,230
disagree with him.

1020
00:40:33,310 --> 00:40:34,800
Otherwise, people will say

1021
00:40:34,800 --> 00:40:36,030
that at the end of my term,

1022
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:36,710
I'm being

1023
00:40:37,350 --> 00:40:38,350
irresponsible

1024
00:40:38,940 --> 00:40:39,900
and reckless.

1025
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:41,070
It's hard for me to explain,

1026
00:40:41,070 --> 00:40:41,550
isn't it?

1027
00:40:41,550 --> 00:40:43,010
Yes, Uncle Lin,

1028
00:40:43,110 --> 00:40:43,870
I understand

1029
00:40:43,900 --> 00:40:44,900
everything you said.

1030
00:40:44,900 --> 00:40:46,180
I sympathize with you.

1031
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:47,720
I really don't want
to make things difficult,

1032
00:40:47,720 --> 00:40:48,550
but the current environment...

1033
00:40:48,550 --> 00:40:49,550
Personally,

1034
00:40:50,510 --> 00:40:51,640
I really don't care.

1035
00:40:52,760 --> 00:40:53,500
You can ask

1036
00:40:53,530 --> 00:40:54,930
the citizens of Tianduo.

1037
00:40:55,300 --> 00:40:56,130
Ask them

1038
00:40:56,930 --> 00:40:59,220
and see whether more people
support the coal mine

1039
00:40:59,220 --> 00:41:00,420
or oppose it.

1040
00:41:02,650 --> 00:41:03,460
I believe,

1041
00:41:04,250 --> 00:41:05,980
since they all benefit from it,

1042
00:41:07,110 --> 00:41:08,440
most of them support it.

1043
00:41:12,920 --> 00:41:15,120
You'll be transferred sooner or later.

1044
00:41:15,560 --> 00:41:17,380
As a reporter from the provincial capital,

1045
00:41:17,380 --> 00:41:18,830
writing a few reports here

1046
00:41:18,830 --> 00:41:19,690
is easy for you.

1047
00:41:20,160 --> 00:41:21,480
But if you leave,

1048
00:41:22,070 --> 00:41:23,030
who will deal

1049
00:41:23,060 --> 00:41:24,460
with the remaining mess?

1050
00:41:25,260 --> 00:41:26,150
It will still be us,

1051
00:41:26,150 --> 00:41:28,210
the officials and people of Tianduo.

1052
00:41:35,210 --> 00:41:36,360
You've come to me

1053
00:41:36,710 --> 00:41:38,440
about this many times already.

1054
00:41:38,630 --> 00:41:39,300
In that case,

1055
00:41:39,300 --> 00:41:40,610
let's be frank.

1056
00:41:41,880 --> 00:41:43,880
Don't take offense at my bluntness.

1057
00:41:44,380 --> 00:41:44,920
As long as I

1058
00:41:44,920 --> 00:41:46,360
hold this position,

1059
00:41:46,950 --> 00:41:48,490
I will still block

1060
00:41:49,820 --> 00:41:51,220
such reports like yours.

1061
00:42:02,530 --> 00:42:04,910
[Tianduo Deji Hospital]

1062
00:42:08,710 --> 00:42:09,230
You're in so much pain,

1063
00:42:09,230 --> 00:42:10,560
yet you can still smile.

1064
00:42:11,560 --> 00:42:12,820
Who would have thought

1065
00:42:12,960 --> 00:42:14,290
that the exchange expert at our hospital

1066
00:42:14,290 --> 00:42:16,360
from Beijing would be you?

1067
00:42:18,690 --> 00:42:19,620
Liu Sen.

1068
00:42:19,760 --> 00:42:21,960
You didn't even tell me you were coming.

1069
00:42:22,040 --> 00:42:23,840
Are your wife and kid in Beijing?

1070
00:42:24,150 --> 00:42:25,410
I brought them with me.

1071
00:42:25,710 --> 00:42:27,300
I have to stay
at Tianduo People's Hospital

1072
00:42:27,300 --> 00:42:28,400
for at least 3 years.

1073
00:42:28,400 --> 00:42:29,470
That's great.

1074
00:42:29,860 --> 00:42:31,360
You're a local, after all.

1075
00:42:33,280 --> 00:42:34,680
What's so great about it?

1076
00:42:36,010 --> 00:42:36,650
Ms. Zhang.

1077
00:42:37,230 --> 00:42:37,580
Your

1078
00:42:37,610 --> 00:42:38,800
herniated disc

1079
00:42:38,860 --> 00:42:39,790
is very serious.

1080
00:42:39,880 --> 00:42:40,500
I'll prescribe you

1081
00:42:40,500 --> 00:42:41,920
a course of physical therapy.

1082
00:42:41,920 --> 00:42:43,040
Do it for a few days in a row

1083
00:42:43,040 --> 00:42:44,640
to reduce the inflammation.

1084
00:42:45,710 --> 00:42:46,960
Back then,

1085
00:42:47,130 --> 00:42:48,200
conditions were tough.

1086
00:42:48,200 --> 00:42:49,400
The work was intense,

1087
00:42:49,730 --> 00:42:51,710
and you didn't use your hips correctly.

1088
00:42:51,710 --> 00:42:53,050
As you get older,

1089
00:42:53,210 --> 00:42:55,010
it might affect your daily life.

1090
00:42:55,820 --> 00:42:57,480
This is an old problem.

1091
00:42:57,500 --> 00:42:58,150
I'm fine.

1092
00:42:58,180 --> 00:42:59,900
You shouldn't take it lightly.

1093
00:42:59,900 --> 00:43:01,000
The worst case back then

1094
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:02,000
was County Mayor Duojie.

1095
00:43:02,000 --> 00:43:02,840
His herniated disc

1096
00:43:02,840 --> 00:43:04,110
compressed his nerves.

1097
00:43:04,110 --> 00:43:05,600
His legs would go numb.

1098
00:43:07,190 --> 00:43:09,080
You know about that?
